**Dog** | Unaligned Align
__Basics__
During Night 1, the Dog may choose between town crier, cursed civilian or wolf, and will immediately become this role for the rest of the game.
__Details__
Choosing a role is an immediate ability. If the Dog hasnâ€™t chosen a role before the night ends, the dog will become a cursed civilian. After choosing a role the Dog is no longer unaligned.

__Simplified__
During Night 1, the Dog may choose between town crier, cursed civilian or wolf, and will immediately become this role for the rest of the game.